OL,3,CPolice officer denies taking pictures
OL,4,Cof corpse from body-worn footage
OL,6,FA volunteer police officer denied
OL,7,Fsharing crime scene pictures and
OL,8,Ftaking photographs of body-worn camera
OL,9,Ffootage showing a corpse.
OL,11,FWilliam Heggs, 23, is accused of
OL,12,Faccessing footage of William Harty,
OL,13,Fwho was killed by his brother-in-law
OL,14,Foutside his home in October 2021, and
OL,15,Ftaking pictures of it on his personal
OL,16,Fmobile phone while he worked as a
OL,17,Fspecial constable for Leicestershire
OL,18,FPolice.
