OL,3,CPolice officer denies taking pictures
OL,4,Cof corpse from body-worn footage
OL,6,FThe defendant appeared at Leicester
OL,7,FCrown Court on Monday with 13 charges
OL,8,Ffollowing an investigation by the
OL,9,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct
OL,10,F(IOPC), which began in November 2021.
OL,12,FHe pleaded not guilty to one charge of
OL,13,Fmisconduct in a public office, nine
OL,14,Foffences of unauthorised computer
OL,15,Faccess and three charges of knowingly
OL,16,For recklessly obtaining or disclosing
OL,17,Fpersonal data, all alleged between
OL,18,FDecember 2020 and December 2021.
