OL,3,CPolice officer denies taking pictures
OL,4,Cof corpse from body-worn footage
OL,6,FThe court heard that Heggs accessed
OL,7,Femails with details about road traffic
OL,8,Fcollisions, took videos and
OL,9,Fphotographs of body-worn camera
OL,10,Ffootage and took photographs of police
OL,11,Fcomputer screens showing police
OL,12,Fintelligence and personal data.
OL,14,FThe second charge on his indictment
OL,15,Falleges that between October 24 2021
OL,16,Fand November 14 2021, Heggs took
OL,17,Fphotographs of video footage showing
OL,18,FMr Harty, who had been killed in a
OL,19,Ffight.
