OL,3,CPolice officer denies taking pictures
OL,4,Cof corpse from body-worn footage
OL,6,FMr Harty, 28, was taken from Bedale
OL,7,FDrive in Leicester to a hospital on
OL,8,FOctober 25 2021 with head injuries,
OL,9,Fwhere he died the following morning.
OL,11,FThe victim's brother-in-law, Martin
OL,12,FCasey, admitted manslaughter and was
OL,13,Fjailed for three years and four months
OL,14,Fin May 2022.
OL,16,FJudge Timothy Spencer KC said to
OL,17,FHeggs, who stood in the dock wearing a
OL,18,Fdark suit: "You appreciate by now, Mr
OL,19,FHeggs, you are in a very, very serious
OL,20,Fposition. These are very serious
OL,21,Fcharges.
